+and
+`G_leak(P_n; I) = (L_tot, L_mirror, L_companion, L_feedback, L_cross)` with
+`(L_tot, L_mirror, L_companion, L_feedback, L_cross) <= (1/4, 1/12, 1/12, 1/16, 1/24)`.
